Description: A SPARQL endpoint of Taiwan Indigenous People provides Taiwan Indigenous people information- including 6 major subjects : [Ethnic](http://lod.apc.gov.tw:8890/schemas/Ethnic_Introduction/)- [Culture](http://lod.apc.gov.tw:8890/schemas/Cultural_Creative/)- [Travel](http://lod.apc.gov.tw:8890/schemas/Travel/)- [Gourmet](http://lod.apc.gov.tw:8890/schemas/Gourmet/)- [Ceremony](http://lod.apc.gov.tw:8890/schemas/Ceremony/) and [Business] (http://lod.apc.gov.tw:8890/schemas/Business/).
